Our pricing philosophy

We know we could charge much more, all other reviews apps do.

But we keep Judge.me fair and accessible because every store, big or small, deserves the best review app.

Our goal isn’t just affordability; it’s delivering unmatched value.

That’s why we invest in constant innovation, helping you collect, manage, and showcase reviews effortlessly.

With Judge.me, pricing is simple: two plans, one flat price, no hidden fees and no scaling costs.

Whether you're just starting out or processing thousands of orders, you get the same powerful features without worrying about rising costs.
